<item>
 <title>Percepções sobre ciência aberta e colaborativa</title>
 <link>http://cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/blog/1509/percep%C3%A7%C3%B5es-sobre-ci%C3%AAncia-aberta-e-colaborativa</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/sites/cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/files/images/tropixel-IMG_0430.JPG&quot; /&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Entrevistas em video com participantes selecionados&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maira Begali [&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jHL-YyTkKCo&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;v&amp;iacute;deo&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Jorge Machado [&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NlrCDeTsKO0&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;v&amp;iacute;deo&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Jutta Machado [&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4fYSacHBjPs&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;v&amp;iacute;deo&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Felipe Spina [&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VLrizmH6z9U&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;v&amp;iacute;deo&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Filipe e Marritza [&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m5EQ9leJq90&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;v&amp;iacute;deo&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Andre Apel e Capi Etheriel [&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LaZcehrNnsQ&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;v&amp;iacute;deo-1&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=beMWOHrxZ4k&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;v&amp;iacute;deo-2&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Survey: Pr&amp;aacute;ticas e percep&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre Ci&amp;ecirc;ncia Aberta&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Question&amp;aacute;rios utilizados&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Question&amp;aacute;rio 1 Oficina Hardware Cientifico. Instrumento de pesquisa do Projeto Ci&amp;ecirc;ncia Aberta Ubatuba, aplicado durante as oficinas de hardware livre, realizadas durante o Tropixel Ci&amp;ecirc;ncia Aberta Ubatuba em junho de 2015: &lt;a href=&quot;http://cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/sites/cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/files/anexos/Questionario-1-Oficina-Hardware-Cientifico.pdf&quot;&gt;http://cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/sites/cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/files/anexos/Questionario-1-Oficina-Hardware-Cientifico.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Question&amp;aacute;rio 2 Painel Ci&amp;ecirc;ncia Aberta. Instrumento de pesquisa do Projeto Ci&amp;ecirc;ncia Aberta Ubatuba, aplicado no dia 3 de junho durante o Painel Ci&amp;ecirc;ncia Aberta no evento Tropixel realizado no audit&amp;oacute;rio do Aqu&amp;aacute;rio de Ubatuba: &lt;a href=&quot;http://http://cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/sites/cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/files/anexos/Questionario-2-Painel-Ciencia-Aberta.pdf&quot;&gt;http://cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/sites/cienciaaberta.ubatuba.cc/files/anexos/Questionario-2-Painel-Ciencia-Aberta.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
